### Llama-2-7b
Prompt: "Given this song:\n\n [song] \n\n Very brifely describe the core emotions and the mood the song conveys. Keep it short. \n\n"

#### Let it snow

The core emotions of the song are:

* Longing for warmth and comfort during a cold and stormy night
* Reluctance to leave the warmth and comfort of the fireplace
* Love and affection for the person by the fire
* Desire to be close and hold each other tight

The mood of the song is cozy, intimate, and romantic.
